translations: 仿制品（dummy 的名词复数）

sentences.sentence: The bottles of whisky on display are all dummies.
sentences.translation: 所陈列的威士忌酒都是假的。

sentences.sentence: Our dummies’ guide will help you make full use of free online lectures.
sentences.translation: 网络学习“傻瓜入门指南”，可以帮助你充分利用免费的网络课程资源。

sentences.sentence: Microsoft's latest products mean that its users should no longer double as crash-test dummies.
sentences.translation: 微软最新产品的问世，意味着用户无须继续充当“碰撞试验”中的假人了。
